item.title: CVE-2023-0769|2024-01-16T15:56:25.178Z -- unknown -- hiweb%20migration%20simple
item.description: The hiWeb Migration Simple WordPress plugin through 2.0.0.1 does not sanitise and escape a parameter before outputting it back in the page, leading to a Reflected Cross-Site Scripting which could be used against high-privilege users such as admins.
